data.title: Wiz Khalifa Settles Suit Over Cannabis Venture
data.meta_description: Rapper Wiz Khalifa has settled a lawsuit filed by the co-owner of his cannabis enterprise who claimed he was cut out of a $20 million deal to license the artist's name and likeness to promote cannabis products.
